  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(String projectNumber, String name, BuildingType buildingType, int erfNumber, Address address, double totalPrice, double totalPaid, ProjectManager projectManager, StructuralEngineer structuralEngineer, Architect architect, Contractor contractor, Customer customer, Date deadline, Date startDate, Date completionDate)
      Constructor for Project.
      Parameters:
      projectNumber - The Project's Number (Acts as an Identifier).
      name - The Name of the Project.
      buildingType - The Building Type of this Project.
      erfNumber - The ERF Number used to ensure the Address is Correct.
      address - The Address Where the Project is Located At.
      totalPrice - The Total Price of the Project.
      totalPaid - The Total Amount the Customer has Paid.
      projectManager - The Project Manager associated with this Project.
      structuralEngineer - The Structural Engineer associated with this Project.
      architect - The Architect associated with this Project.
      contractor - The Contractor associated with this Project.
      customer - The Customer associated with this Project.
      deadline - The Date when the Project must be Completed By.
      startDate - The Date work has Started on the Project (can be Null if Work was not started yet).
      completionDate - The Date the Project has been Completed (can be Null if the Project is not Completed).
